# LandWatch — Final Walkthrough

LandWatch is a premium, secure, and transparent digital platform for land litigation lookup and case tracking.

## All Features Delivered ✅

| Category | Features |
|----------|----------|
| **Search** | Village + Survey Number, **Autocomplete Suggestions**, **Ctrl+K Shortcut** |
| **Land Data** | Holder details, **Ownership History timeline**, **Risk Score (Low/Med/High)** |
| **Court Data** | Judge details (prominent cards), **Ongoing/Disposed tags**, Petitioner/Respondent parties |
| **User Rights** | Public/Lawyer Register & Login, **My Cases (Lawyers)**, **Reveal Sensitive Data** |
| **Updates** | **SMS/Email Alerts subscription**, Case timeline updates |
| **Admin** | Full dashboard, **Verify status toggle**, **Record Editing modal**, Audit Trail |
| **UX** | **Print Case Details**, Dark modern theme, Responsive design, Micro-animations |

## 🚀 Key Features in Action

### 1. Advanced Search & Autocomplete
Users can quickly find villages with real-time suggestions and use **Ctrl+K** to focus search from anywhere.

![Autocomplete Search Suggestions](file:///C:/Users/tamil/.gemini/antigravity/brain/de7fa1dd-29cf-4cf9-a0fb-c2dd35af1cd5/complete_demo_1771741913754.png)

### 2. Transparent Case Records (With Reveal & Print)
Land records now feature **"Reveal"** buttons for masked data (Aadhaar/PAN) and a **"Print"** button to export case details.

![Aadhaar Data Revealed](file:///C:/Users/tamil/.gemini/antigravity/brain/de7fa1dd-29cf-4cf9-a0fb-c2dd35af1cd5/aadhaar_revealed_1771744165210.png)

### 3. Comprehensive Admin Dashboard
Admins have full control to verify records, update data in a secure modal, and monitor system activity via the audit trail.

![Admin Table with Edit Tools](file:///C:/Users/tamil/.gemini/antigravity/brain/de7fa1dd-29cf-4cf9-a0fb-c2dd35af1cd5/admin_updated_table_1771744353629.png)

![Edit Record Modal](file:///C:/Users/tamil/.gemini/antigravity/brain/de7fa1dd-29cf-4cf9-a0fb-c2dd35af1cd5/edit_modal_land_record_1771744258761.png)

